data.description: Welcome to an absolutely GORGEOUS single-story home in the sought-after 55+ community of Wellspring @ Tamarron! The gated entryway leads to a kitchen & living area that is spacious, light & bright, providing a vibrant atmosphere for friends & family. The picturesque view of the beautifully landscaped large back yard is framed by double sliding glass doors. With a walking path located behind the home, there are even more trees to grace the view. Custom made window treatments with magnets offer privacy when desired. The extended covered back patio has 2 ceiling fans, with shade in the afternoon to enjoy our beautiful Texas nights. The Study/Office is currently being used as a Dining room. The home has wider doorways to allow room for a walker or wheelchair. Generous sized bedrooms, with the Primary larger...Primary closet is GINORMOUS!! Wellspring has its own community center, with a clubhouse & LOTS of activities. Tamarron has a Gym, dog park & dual pools + splashpad for all residents.
